SUMMARY:60th Anniversary Gala
DESCRIPTION:  \nMay 15\, 2026\n \nBuy Tickets \nFrom protecting native plants to inspiring generations of visitors\, the Garden continues to grow because of you. Join us for an evening of celebration as we honor what we’ve accomplished and share our vision for the future: where science\, engagement\, and conservation come together with purpose and possibility. \nHonorary Chairs\nRitch & Susan Allison\nFrank & Ellen Proctor\nMike & Melissa Raley \n \n  \n \n  \nPlanning Committee\nGail Perry\nJordan Barratt\nBetsy Bennett\nMay Bryan\nVirginia Buysse\nMelanie Christian\nEliza Cook\nHelen Frankstone\nKim Fraser\nPat Holder\nKatherine Kopp\nMia Pizzagalli\nSue Plambeck\nLiza Roberts \n \nEvent Hosts\nLongleaf\nAlice & John May\nFrank & Ellen Proctor \nMagnolia\nRitch & Susan Allison\nRufus & Linda Edmisten\nKate & Jeff Hedges\nJeff Mason\nSue & Charles Plambeck\nJennifer & Al Runquist\nPhyllis Thomas & Alan Curtis\nDamon Waitt \nSassafras\nBetsy & Walter Bennett\nBecky & Munroe Cobey\nNicholas & Amy Penwarden\nGail Perry & Bill Cobb\nMia Pizzagalli & Ken Shelton\nMike & Melissa Raley \nDogwood\nMike & Mary Andrews\nPaula Noell & Palmer Page\nSims Preston & Olympia Stone\nKader & Margaret Ramsey\nCarol Tresolini & Tom Fiore \nFor information on becoming an Event Host see this link or contact Stephen Keith at 919-962-9458. \nBuy Tickets
URL:https://ncbg.unc.edu/event/60th-anniversary-gala/
LOCATION:The Barn at Fearrington Village\, 2000 Fearrington Village Center\, Pittsboro\, 27312\, United States
END:VEVENT
